   <narrative xml:lang="EN">North-East Syria Response (SYR-0002)</narrative>
  </title>
  <description type="1">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">This response seeks to support displaced people fleeing conflict in in the north-east and north-west of Syria.   The response involves 1) a needs assessment, to inform the response by Oxfam and other agencies, 2) the provision of emergency WASH and non-food items to support livelihoods, and 3) the implementation of more durable solutions for WASH services (e.g. spot rehabilitation of water supply pipeline) and support for diversified livelihoods opportunities to increase resilience.</narrative>
  </description>
